! Cupboard
![#COMPATIBILITY] - START
if iFunctions = -1 then gosub "CupboardCompatibility" endif
![#COMPATIBILITY] - END
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 THEN END IF not(gs_shadow) THEN SHADOW OFF
!* 3D Hotspot unID=1
!* Total Height
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot A, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, B, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, B, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, B, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot A, B, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A, B, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A, B, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
!* Leg Height
hotspot cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), cooh+fr_th1, 0, unID, leg_h, 1 : unID=unID+1 hotspot cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), cooh+fr_th1, -1, unID, leg_h, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), cooh+fr_th1, leg_h, unID, leg_h, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot A-cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), cooh+fr_th1, 0, unID, leg_h, 1 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A-cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), cooh+fr_th1, -1, unID, leg_h, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A-cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), cooh+fr_th1, leg_h, unID, leg_h, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot A-cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), B, 0, unID, leg_h, 1 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A-cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), B, -1, unID, leg_h, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A-cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), B, leg_h, unID, leg_h, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), B, 0, unID, leg_h, 1 : unID=unID+1 hotspot cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), B, -1, unID, leg_h, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot cooh*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), B, leg_h, unID, leg_h, 2 : unID=unID+1
!!**************************************************
ADD a/2,b,0
PEN gs_cont_pen
MULX -1
thickness = 0.02 lffw=a-2*cooh-2*thickness/2 !!! Leafs full widht lffh=zzyzx-cot-leg_h-2*thickness/2 !!! Leafs full height
!* Detailed 3D
CALL "fa_cabinet_credenza_CS_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL b=b-fr_th1
!*Cornices
MULX -1 ADDZ zzyzx-cot
CALL "fa_cornicetyp_CS_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL
DEL 1 DEL 1
!* Legs
CALL "fa_cabinet_legtyp_CS_WMCC" PARAMETERS a=a,b=b-fr_th1,gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_leg_type_m=gs_leg_type_m,leg_h=leg_h,leg_w=leg_w, cooh=cooh,gs_resol=gs_resol,gs_leg_mat=gs_leg_mat, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen,gs_lining_m=gs_lining_m
!* Shelves and Hangers
corniceRight = 0 corniceLeft = 0 if gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT or gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH then corniceRight = 1 if gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT or gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH then corniceLeft = 1 insideA = A - cooh*corniceRight - cooh*corniceLeft - 2*thickness if iFunctions = COMBINED then insideTemp = insideA if dn >= 3 then insideA = ((insideA-thickness*(dn-1))/dn)*(dn-2)+thickness*(dn-3) else insideA = (insideA-thickness)/2 endif endif if iFunctions = SHELVES or iFunctions = COMBINED then sfh=zzyzx-cot-leg_h-2*thickness !!! Shelves full height bb=(sfh+thickness)/(shn+1) add -a/2+thickness+cooh*corniceLeft, -thickness,leg_h + bb if iFunctions = SHELVES then gosub "shelves" else addx insideTemp - insideA gosub "shelves" del 1 endif del 1 endif
if iFunctions = COMBINED and dn < 3 then add -a/2+thickness+cooh*corniceLeft, -thickness,leg_h+thickness addx insideA material shmat PRISM_ 4, sfh, thickness,0,15, thickness,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15, 0,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15, 0,0,15 del 2 endif
if iFunctions = HANGERS or iFunctions = COMBINED then material gs_hanger_mat ADD -a/2+thickness+cooh*corniceLeft, -b/2, (zzyzx - cot)/10*8.5 if iFunctions = HANGERS then roty 90 cylind insideA, thickness del 1 else addx insideTemp - insideA - thickness roty 270 cylind insideTemp - insideA -thickness, thickness del 2 endif del 1 endif
!* Vertical panels
IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_NONE OR gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_NONE then valt2=-a/2+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH then valt2=-a/2+cooh+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT then valt2=-a/2+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT then valt2=-a/2+cooh+thickness/2
vpn=CEIL(dn/2)-1
ADD valt2+(lffw2/dn)*2,-thickness,leg_h+thickness
FOR i=1 TO vpn MATERIAL gs_cabinet_mat PRISM_ 4, zzyzx-cot-leg_h-2*thickness, thickness/2,0,15, -thickness/2,0,15, -thickness/2,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15, thickness/2,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15 ADDX (lffw2/dn)*2 NEXT i DEL vpn DEL 1
!* Leafs
ADD valt2,-b+fr_th1+cooh,leg_h+thickness/2 FOR i=1 TO dn call "fa_warddoortyp_CS_WMCC" parameters all bNotMacro = 0, gs_full_edit = 0, bAngleEdit = 0, bMirrored = 0, bFormMirror = 0, bSliding = 0, iDoorStyle = iDoorStyle, iTempDoorStyle = iDoorStyle, bBevel = gs_bevel, doorThickness = fr_th1, doorFrameWidth = doorframe_w, mullionWidth = 0.016, nVerticalMullion = vert_gnum, nHorizontalMullion = hor_gnum, matDoorFrame = doorframe_mat, matDoorGlass = doorglas_mat, matDoorMirror = doorglas_mat, matDoorDecor1 = doorframe_mat, matDoorDecor2 = doorframe_mat, doorWidth = lffw2/dn, doorHeight = lffh, doorCustomPanelName = gs_cust_p, gs_knob_type_m = 0, doorAngle3D = 0
ADDX lffw2/dn NEXT i DEL dn DEL 1
!* Knobs on leafs
valt=-a/2+cooh+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT then valt=-a/2+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT then valt=-a/2+cooh+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_NONE then valt=-a/2+thickness/2
ADD valt,-b+fr_th1+cooh,leg_h+thickness/2
IF gs_knob_p_m=0 OR gs_knob_type_m=1 OR gs_knob_type_m=2 OR gs_knob_type_m=3 THEN temp = 0 ELSE temp = knob_size ENDIF
IF INT(dn/2)<>dn/2 THEN ADD lffw2-lffw2/dn+knob_pl_x+temp, -fr_th1, knob_pl_y
CALL "fa_knobtyp_CS_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL
add -temp, 0, -knob_pl_y hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_y, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, knob_pl_y, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_y, 2 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1 Addx -knob_pl_x - temp hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot knob_pl_x, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 2 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1 DEL 1 ENDIF
h_knob=1-leg_h-thickness/2
ADD lffw2/dn-(doorframe_w-fr_th1)/2*0,0,knob_pl_y FOR k=1 TO INT(dn/2) FOR s=1 TO 2 add knob_pl_x + temp,-fr_th1,0
CALL "fa_knobtyp_CS_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL
add -temp, 0, -knob_pl_y hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_y, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, knob_pl_y, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_y, 2 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1 addx -knob_pl_x - temp hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot knob_pl_x, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 2 : unID=unID+1 del 1
del 1 MULX -1 ! ADD -(doorframe_w-fr_th1)-knob_pl_x+0.05,fr_th1,0 NEXT s DEL 2 ADD lffw2/dn*2,0,0 NEXT k DEL INT(dn)/2 DEL 1
if dn/2-int(dn/2)<0.001 then del 1
IF dn<>1 THEN DEL 1
END
"shelves": FOR i=1 TO shn MATERIAL shmat PRISM_ 4, thickness, insideA,0,15, insideA,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15, 0,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15, 0,0,15 ADDZ bb NEXT i DEL shn return
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Cupboard.gsm
![#COMPATIBILITY] - START
if iFunctions = -1 then gosub "CupboardCompatibility" endif
![#COMPATIBILITY] - END PEN gs_cont_pen
CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0,b, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a/2,b, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a/2,b/2, unID : unID = unID + 1
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! *** Minimal space *** !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! call "fa_minimalspace_CS_WMCC" parameters all MSType = 1, unID = 3000
FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_b 5,7, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,1, a,0,1, a,b,1, 0,b,1, 0,0,-1
!!!Functions
if iFunctions = HANGERS then LINE2 0,b/2,a,b/2 tempA = a gosub "hangers" endif
if iFunctions = COMBINED then if dn >= 3 then insideA = (A/dn)*(dn-2) else insideA = A/2 LINE2 a/2,0,a/2,b endif
LINE2 insideA,b/2,A,b/2 ADD2 insideA,0 LINE2 0,0,0,b tempA = a-insideA gosub "hangers" DEL 1 endif
!!! Style 1 !!!
IF iSymbolStyle = SYMB_STYLE_1 THEN
ADD2 -a/dn*2,0
FOR i=1 TO CEIL(dn/2-1) LINE2 a,0,a,b ADD2 -a/dn*2,0 NEXT i DEL CEIL(dn/2-1)
DEL 1
ENDIF
!!! Style 2 !!!
IF iSymbolStyle = SYMB_STYLE_2 THEN
ADD2 -a/dn*2,0
FOR i=1 TO CEIL(dn/2-1) LINE2 a,0,a,b ADD2 -a/dn*2,0 NEXT i DEL CEIL(dn/2-1)
DEL 1
FOR i=1 TO INT(dn/2) LINE2 a,0,a-a/dn*2,b LINE2 a-a/dn*2,0,a,b ADD2 -a/dn*2,0 NEXT i DEL INT(dn/2)
IF INT(dn/2)<>dn/2 THEN LINE2 0,0,a/dn,b LINE2 a/dn,0,0,b ENDIF
ENDIF
!!! Style 3 !!!
IF iSymbolStyle = SYMB_STYLE_3 THEN
ADD2 -a/dn*2,0
FOR i=1 TO CEIL(dn/2-1) LINE2 a,0,a,b ADD2 -a/dn*2,0 NEXT i DEL CEIL(dn/2-1)
DEL 1
FOR i=1 TO INT(dn/2) LINE2 a,b,a-a/dn,0 LINE2 a-a/dn,0,a-a/dn*2,b ADD2 -a/dn*2,0 NEXT i DEL INT(dn/2)
IF INT(dn/2)<>dn/2 THEN LINE2 0,0,a/dn,b ENDIF
ENDIF
!!! Style 4-5 !!!
IF iSymbolStyle = SYMB_STYLE_4 OR iSymbolStyle = SYMB_STYLE_5 THEN
ADD2 -a/dn,0
FOR i=1 TO dn LINE2 a,0,a,0.025 ADD2 -a/dn,0 NEXT i DEL dn
DEL 1
LINE2 0,0.025,a,0.025
ENDIF
!!! Style 5-6 !!!
IF iSymbolStyle = SYMB_STYLE_5 OR iSymbolStyle = SYMB_STYLE_6 THEN
IF INT(dn/2)<>dn/2 THEN nn=1 IF INT(dn/2)=dn/2 THEN nn=0
ADD2 a/dn*nn,0
FOR i=1 TO INT(dn/2)
ARC2 0,0,a/dn,360-opa2,0 LINE2 0,0,COS(opa2)*a/dn,0-SIN(opa2)*a/dn
ARC2 2*a/dn,0,a/dn,180,180+opa2 LINE2 2*a/dn,0,2*a/dn-COS(opa2)*a/dn,0-SIN(opa2)*a/dn
ADD2 a/dn*2,0 NEXT i DEL INT(dn/2)
DEL 1
IF INT(dn/2)<>dn/2 THEN ARC2 0,0,a/dn,360-opa2,0 LINE2 0,0,COS(opa2)*a/dn,0-SIN(opa2)*a/dn ENDIF ENDIF
END
"hangers": ADD2 0.2, (b-0.025)/2 hn = tempA - 2*0.1 cn=INT(hn/0.15) FOR ii=1 TO cn ff=rnd(.2) ROT2 ff*100 line2 -0.025, -0.2, 0.025, 0.2 DEL 1 ADD2 0.15, 0 NEXT ii DEL cn del 1 return
